 of HTMs (by up to\n2.59x), and other HyTMs (by up to 1.55x) for SSCA2 graph benchmark running on a\nmulticore machine with a large shared memory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 03:21:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2017 19:05:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-06"}
