oarse grid, where each equation represents one\nof the continua on the fine grid. We present various basis construction\nmechanisms and numerical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 04:43:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-24"}
